			"type":"text",
			"text":"# SIUE Courses\n\n## Courses List\n- [ECE](https://www.siue.edu/academics/undergraduate/courses/index.shtml?subject=ECE)\n- [MATH](https://www.siue.edu/academics/undergraduate/courses/index.shtml?subject=MATH)\n- [CS](https://www.siue.edu/academics/undergraduate/courses/index.shtml?subject=CS)\n- [IE](https://www.siue.edu/academics/undergraduate/courses/index.shtml?subject=IE)\n- [PHYS](https://www.siue.edu/academics/undergraduate/courses/index.shtml?subject=PHYS)\n\n## Note\n- Physics department is eliminated. Teach out is taking in place until 2029. I need to figure out whether I can somehow take optics/photonics courses during the teach out phase.",
